Step 1: Create Account

Open:

EmailJS Sign Up

Sign up using Gmail
Login to dashboard
Step 2: Add Email Service

Open:

EmailJS Email Services

Then:

Click Add New Service
Select Gmail
Connect your Gmail account
Give service name

After creation you will see:

service_xxxxxxx

Example:

service_ab12cd3

This is your:

YOUR_SERVICE_ID
Step 3: Create Email Template

Open:

EmailJS Templates

Click Create New Template
Add:

Subject:

Your OTP Code

Message:

Hello,

Your OTP is: {{otp_code}}

Thank You

Save template.

Then you will get:

template_xxxxxx

Example:

template_hj82ks1

This is your:

YOUR_TEMPLATE_ID
Step 4: Get Public Key

Open:

EmailJS Account Settings

Scroll down.

You will see:

Public Key

Example:

abcdEFGHijk12345

This is your:

YOUR_PUBLIC_KEY
Final Example

Replace this:

emailjs.init("YOUR_PUBLIC_KEY");

with:

emailjs.init("abcdEFGHijk12345");

Replace:

"YOUR_SERVICE_ID"

with:

"service_ab12cd3"

Replace:

"YOUR_TEMPLATE_ID"

with:

"template_hj82ks1"
Final Working Example
emailjs.init("abcdEFGHijk12345");

emailjs.send(
   "service_ab12cd3",
   "template_hj82ks1",
   templateParams
)
